OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey start with some
OL,6,Fpatchy rain and drizzle. However,
OL,7,Fskies will gradually brighten from the
OL,8,Feast, with an increasingly sunny
OL,9,Fafternoon developing across the
OL,10,Fregion. Feeling cooler than yesterday
OL,11,Fwith an easterly breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine evening with plenty of
OL,14,Flate sunshine. A few mist and fog
OL,15,Fpatches developing overnight but most
OL,16,Fremaining clear. Turning chilly in the
OL,17,Fcountryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
